程序包 ATU_Program

类 Output.Student

java.lang.Object
ATU_Program.Output.Student
封闭类:
Output
public static class Output.Student
extends java.lang.Object
The class is used to save the students information who are from the same team and load them to the table.

      This method is the constructor of the class Student for table input.
      参数:
      Mid - The student id of the input student.
      Mname - The student name of the input student.
      Team_num - The number of the input student's name.
      Memid - The number of the teammate's order.
      Name - The name of the teammates.
      K1 - The k1 energy of the teammates.
      K2 - The k2 energy of the teammates.
